@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Returns 0 on null input.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "idl_field_tag" takes f as Integer returns Integer:
    If f is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Return proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with f, 16
