@Reasoning
Field accessor: label (optional/required/repeated).
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Load offset 24.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Returns 0 on null input.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "idl_field_label" takes f as Integer returns Integer:
